page.title: 18Family Life
page.content: I get up every morning to go to school at 7:30 a.m.I have my breakfast,pack my things and at 8:20 a.m.I go for the bus.The bus is normally late when we get to school,we get "done" for being late.We have registration at 9:00 a.m. then at 9:15 a.m.we go to lessons. Today we have music, craft, maths and then social studies.My best subject is science because you use bunsen burners and other things.We leave school at 3:45 p.m.I have a good paper round for which i get Â£2.70 a week.Tommorow I am sleeping at Daniels in a tent for one night.Then I am going to play cricket for Flixton Juniors.We are playing Sewerby.We will win.
